==English==
===Alternative spellings===
*sometimes hyphenated or expressed as a phrase: '''pan-deistically''', '''pan deistically'''
*sometimes either the P or both the P and the initial T are capitalized: '''Pandeistically''', '''PanDeistically'''
*variations of capitalization and spacing may be combined: '''Pan-deistically''', '''Pan-Deistically''', '''Pan Deistically''', '''Pan deistically'''
===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''[[πάν]]'' (pán) "all"
and {{L.}} ''[[deus]]'' "god"

===Adjective===
{{en-ad|pandeistically}}
# in a [[pandeistic]] manner

